CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 9, 1954, page 3, reads: "Third Term - Mayor David L. Lawrence this week began an unprecedented third term as the city's chief executive. Here he takes oath of office from Common Pleas Court Judge A. Marshall Thompson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Common Pleas Court Judge A. Marshall Thompson swearing in Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence with priest standing nearby in Pittsburgh City Council Chambers at the City Council Building, Downtown
